IDENTIFICATION DIVISION. A. "GotoLoopTest".
DATA DIVISION
01 INDEX PICTURE IS 9.
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
PERFORM A.

A.
    DISPLAY "COUNT" WITH NO ADVANCING.
    GO TO B.
    DISPLAY "Should not reach!".
B.
    LOOP
        VARYING INDEX FROM 1 TO 5 BY 1
        DISPLAY INDEX WITH NO ADVANCING
        EVALUATE INDEX
            WHEN 4
                GO TO C
                DISPLAY "should not display 4"
        END
    END
    .
C.
    DISPLAY "DONE" WITH NO ADVANCING.
